@using ExploreJordan.Settings;
@using System.Security.Claims

@model ExploreJordan.ViewModels.CombinedViewModel

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<link href="~/csspop/aqaba.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Aqaba</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="Popular">
        <h2 style="text-align: center;margin-top:125px;">Aqaba</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="style-0">
        <div class="style-1">
            <div class="style-2">
                <div class="style-3" data-ft="true">
                    <div class="style-4">
                        <div class="style-5">
                            <button aria-label="See all photos" class="style-6">
                                <picture class="style-7">
                                    <img src="~/img2/aqaba/1.jpg" width="720" height="480" role="none" alt="" fetchpriority="high" class="style-11" />
                                </picture>
                            </button><button aria-label="See all photos" class="style-12">
                                <picture class="style-13">
                                    <img src="~/img2/aqaba/2.jpeg" width="720" height="480" role="none" alt="" fetchpriority="high" class="style-17" />
                                </picture>
                            </button><button aria-label="See all photos" class="style-18">
                                <picture class="style-19">
                                    <img src="~/img2/aqaba/3.jpg" width="720" height="480" role="none" alt="" fetchpriority="high" class="style-23" />

                                </picture>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-27"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="style-28">
                <div class="style-29">
                    <section class="style-30">
                        <div data-automation="WebPresentation_ProductAboveTheFoldInfo" class="style-31">
                            <div class="style-32" data-ft="true">
                                <div class="style-33">
                                    <div class="style-34">
                                        <div class="style-35">
                                            <div class="style-36">About</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="style-37">
                                        <div class="style-38">
                                            <div class="style-39">
                                                <div class="style-40"><p>Aqaba, Jordan's only coastal city, is a vibrant and dynamic destination nestled on the shores of the Red Sea. Boasting a rich history dating back thousands of years, stunning natural beauty, and a burgeoning tourism scene, Aqaba offers something for everyone. <p>History and Culture:</p><p>Ancient city: Aqaba's history stretches back to 4000 BC, evident in its archaeological treasures like the Islamic-era Aqaba Fort and the ruins of the ancient city of Ayla. Cultural melting pot: Aqaba's location at the crossroads of trade routes has made it a cultural melting pot, with influences from Arabic, Ottoman, and European cultures evident in its architecture, cuisine, and traditions.Museums and art galleries: The city houses several museums and art galleries showcasing its rich heritage and contemporary art scene.</p><p>Natural Beauty and Activities:</p><p>Breathtaking coastline: Aqaba is renowned for its stunning coral reefs, crystal-clear waters, and pristine beaches, offering unparalleled opportunities for swimming, snorkeling, scuba diving, and other water sports.Spectacular desert landscapes: Aqaba is surrounded by dramatic desert landscapes, perfect for exploring by jeep, camel, or on foot. Visitors can also experience the thrill of sandboarding and dune bashing. Marine parks and wildlife: Aqaba Marine Park is a home to diverse marine life, including colorful coral reefs, exotic fish, and even dolphins. Visitors can also spot a variety of birds at the Aqaba Bird Sanctuary</p><p>Tourism and Entertainment:<p><p>Modern resort city: Aqaba has transformed into a modern resort city, offering luxurious hotels, world-class restaurants, and exciting nightlife.Shopping and dining: The city boasts vibrant bazaars and modern shopping centers, offering a variety of souvenirs, local crafts, and international brands. Aqaba's diverse culinary scene caters to all tastes, with restaurants serving Jordanian, seafood, international, and fusion cuisine.Family-friendly activities: Aqaba offers a variety of activities for families with children, including water parks, amusement parks, and educational centers.</p></p></div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>



    <div class="conwrap">
        @if (Model != null)
        {
            @if (Model.Activities != null)
            {
                @foreach (var activity in Model.Activities)
                {
                    if (activity.City != null && activity.City.Trim().Equals("Aqaba", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
                    {
                        <div class="CarRentalContainer0">
                            <div class="style-00">
                                <div class="style-01">
                                    <div class="style-02">
                                        <div class="style-03">
                                            <div class="style-05">
                                                <span class="style-06">
                                                    <span class="style-07">@activity.Name</span>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="imagesize0">
                                            <img src="@($"{FileSettings.ImagesPath}/{activity.Cover}")" alt="Car Image" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-09">
                                            <div>@activity.Description</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-052">

                                            <span class="style-053">
                                                <span class="style-054">@activity.Price</span>
                                                <span class="style-055">JD</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-051">
                                            <div class="style-056" data-testid="rc-itinerary-cta-button">
                                                <div class="style-057">
                                                    <a asp-controller="Activities" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@activity.Id" class="style-058">
                                                        <div class="style-059">View Deal</div>
                                                    </a>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                }
            }

            @if (Model.Accommodations != null)
            {
                @foreach (var accommodation in Model.Accommodations)
                {
                    if (accommodation.City != null && accommodation.City.Trim().Equals("Aqaba", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
                    {
                        <div class="CarRentalContainer">
                            <div class="style-00">
                                <div class="style-01">
                                    <div class="style-02">
                                        <div class="style-03">
                                            <div class="style-05">
                                                <span class="style-06">
                                                    <span class="style-07">@accommodation.Name</span>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="imagesize0">
                                            <img src="@($"{FileSettings.ImagesPath}/{accommodation.Cover}")" alt="Car Image" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-09">
                                            <div>@accommodation.Description</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-052">

                                            <span class="style-053">
                                                <span class="style-054">@accommodation.Price</span>
                                                <span class="style-055">JD/Day</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-051">
                                            <div class="style-056" data-testid="rc-itinerary-cta-button">
                                                <div class="style-057">
                                                    <a asp-controller="Accommodation" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@accommodation.Id" class="style-058">
                                                        <div class="style-059">View Deal</div>
                                                    </a>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                }
            }

            @if (Model.Tours != null)
            {
                @foreach (var tour in Model.Tours)
                {
                    if (tour.City != null && tour.City.Trim().Equals("Aqaba", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
                    {
                        <div class="CarRentalContainer">
                            <div class="style-00">
                                <div class="style-01">
                                    <div class="style-02">
                                        <div class="style-03">
                                            <div class="style-05">
                                                <span class="style-06">
                                                    <span class="style-07">@tour.Name</span>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="imagesize0">
                                            <img src="@($"{FileSettings.ImagesPath}/{tour.Cover}")" alt="Car Image" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-09">
                                            <div>@tour.Description</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-052">

                                            <span class="style-053">
                                                <span class="style-054">@tour.Price</span>
                                                <span class="style-055">JD</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-051">
                                            <div class="style-056" data-testid="rc-itinerary-cta-button">
                                                <div class="style-057">
                                                    <a asp-controller="Tours" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@tour.Id" class="style-058">
                                                        <div class="style-059">View Deal</div>
                                                    </a>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                }
            }
        }

    </div>
</body>
</html>